  m_text: "a woman's body  \na church  \na bit of imagination\n...\nlisten closely,
    and you may hear  \nthe devil on the move\n\nwhat a beautiful night  \nask anyone
    who's seen darker times:  \nwere the nights back then this beautiful?  \nthey\u2019d
    say,  \n\"unfortunately, there were even better ones\"\n\nwould you still be
    willing  \nto savor the best of nights  \nknowing they come with a \"unfortunately\"?\n\nI
    know you would\nyou already have."
